---
layout: layout.njk
permalink: "/join.html"
title: "Join Us — Quan Zhen Cultural Society · 全真教化協會"
description: "Join Quan Zhen Cultural Society (全真教化協會) — become a member or volunteer with Singapore's Quan Zhen Cultural Society. Register online today."
ogTitle: "Join Us — Quan Zhen Cultural Society"
ogDescription: "Become part of Quan Zhen Cultural Society — join as a member or volunteer with our Singapore Quan Zhen Cultural Society."
bilingualNav: false
showOfferings: false
pageStyle: |
  .page-hero { background: var(--navy-primary); padding: 140px 0 80px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2); }
  .page-hero-inner { max-width: 640px; }
  .page-hero h1 { color: var(--rice-paper); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .page-hero p { color: var(--muted-sky); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; }

  .join-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 64px; }
  .join-card { background: var(--white); border: 0.5px solid rgba(26,39,68,0.1); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .join-card:hover { border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.35); }
  .join-card-head { background: var(--navy-primary); padding: 24px; }
  .join-card-cn { font-family: var(--font-cn); font-size: 20px; color: var(--brass-gold); margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1; }
  .join-card-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--rice-paper); }
  .join-card-body { padding: 24px; }
  .join-card-body p { font-size: 13px; color: #555; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .join-benefits { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .join-benefit { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 12px; color: #444; line-height: 1.5; }
  .benefit-dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--brass-gold); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 6px; }

  .form-section { background: var(--white); border: 0.5px solid rgba(26,39,68,0.1); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .form-section-head { background: var(--navy-primary); padding: 20px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .form-section-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--rice-paper); }
  .form-section-cn { font-family: var(--font-cn); font-size: 12px; color: var(--brass-gold); letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
  .form-section-body { padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; }
  .form-placeholder { background: var(--color-background-secondary, #f8f6f0); border: 1.5px dashed rgba(201,168,76,0.4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 40px 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .form-placeholder-icon { font-family: var(--font-cn); font-size: 32px; color: var(--brass-gold); opacity: 0.5; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .form-placeholder-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--navy-primary); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .form-placeholder-note { font-size: 12px; color: #888; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto 20px; }
  .form-cta-btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 12px 28px; background: var(--brass-gold); color: var(--navy-deep);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .form-cta-btn:hover { background: #b8943e; color: var(--navy-deep); }
  .form-cta-btn svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .form-alt-note { font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 16px; }
  .form-alt-note a { color: var(--brass-gold); text-decoration: underline; }

  .process-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
  .process-step { text-align: center; padding: 20px 12px; }
  .process-number {
    width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--navy-primary); color: var(--brass-gold);
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 12px;
  }
  .process-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--navy-primary); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .process-desc { font-size: 12px; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .join-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .process-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .process-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
---

    <!-- ── Page Hero ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="page-hero-inner">
          <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:12px;">Be part of the tradition · 加入我們</p>
          <span class="cn-text" style="display:block; font-size:13px; margin-bottom:16px;">入會與義工</span>
          <h1>Join Us</h1>
          <p>Whether you are drawn to the practice, the community, or the cultural heritage of Taoism — there is a place for you at Quan Zhen Cultural Society. Join as a member or volunteer with us.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Join Options ───────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="section section-paper">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:12px;">Two ways to get involved</p>
        <h2 style="margin-bottom:6px;">Membership and Volunteering</h2>
        <p class="cn-text" style="font-size:13px; margin-bottom:40px;">會員與義工</p>

        <div class="join-grid">

          <div class="join-card">
            <div class="join-card-head">
              <div class="join-card-cn">入會</div>
              <div class="join-card-title">Become a Member</div>
            </div>
            <div class="join-card-body">
              <p>Membership gives you full access to our community, classes, rituals, and resources. As a member of Quan Zhen Cultural Society, you become part of a living Taoist lineage community in Singapore.</p>
              <div class="join-benefits">
                <div class="join-benefit"><div class="benefit-dot"></div>Access to weekly Sunday scripture classes</div>
                <div class="join-benefit"><div class="benefit-dot"></div>Priority registration for rituals and ceremonies</div>
                <div class="join-benefit"><div class="benefit-dot"></div>Access to learning resources and study materials</div>
                <div class="join-benefit"><div class="benefit-dot"></div>Invitations to members-only events and gatherings</div>
                <div class="join-benefit"><div class="benefit-dot"></div>Be part of a registered Quanzhen Longmen community</div>
              </div>
              <a href="#membership-form" class="btn btn-gold" style="width:100%; justify-content:center;">Apply for membership</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="join-card">
            <div class="join-card-head">
              <div class="join-card-cn">義工</div>
              <div class="join-card-title">Volunteer with Us</div>
            </div>
            <div class="join-card-body">
              <p>Our volunteers are the backbone of everything we do — from setting up for rituals to supporting events, managing social media, and helping new members feel welcome. No experience needed, just willingness.</p>
              <div class="join-benefits">
                <div class="join-benefit"><div class="benefit-dot"></div>Support rituals and ceremonial events</div>
                <div class="join-benefit"><div class="benefit-dot"></div>Event setup, logistics, and coordination</div>
                <div class="join-benefit"><div class="benefit-dot"></div>Photography, videography, and social media</div>
                <div class="join-benefit"><div class="benefit-dot"></div>Administrative and community support</div>
                <div class="join-benefit"><div class="benefit-dot"></div>Teaching assistant roles for scripture classes</div>
              </div>
              <a href="#volunteer-form" class="btn btn-outline-gold" style="width:100%; justify-content:center;">Register as volunteer</a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Membership process -->
        <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:24px;">How membership works</p>
        <div class="process-grid" style="margin-bottom:64px;">
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-number">1</div>
            <div class="process-title">Submit enquiry</div>
            <p class="process-desc">Fill in the membership enquiry form below — tell us a little about yourself and your interest in Taoism.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-number">2</div>
            <div class="process-title">We get in touch</div>
            <p class="process-desc">A committee member will reach out via email within a few days to answer any questions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-number">3</div>
            <div class="process-title">Come for a visit</div>
            <p class="process-desc">We invite you to join a Sunday class or an upcoming event — so you can experience the community before committing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-number">4</div>
            <div class="process-title">Complete registration</div>
            <p class="process-desc">Once you're ready, complete your formal membership registration and payment to become an official member.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Membership enquiry form -->
        <div class="form-section" id="membership-form">
          <div class="form-section-head">
            <div>
              <div class="form-section-title">Membership Enquiry</div>
              <div class="form-section-cn">入會查詢</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-section-body">
            <div class="form-placeholder">
              <div class="form-placeholder-icon">入</div>
              <div class="form-placeholder-title">Membership Enquiry Form</div>
              <p class="form-placeholder-note">
                Click the button below to open the membership enquiry form. Your response will be sent directly to our committee and stored securely in our Google Workspace.
              </p>
              <a href="https://forms.gle/L2YyKX4mVq21LhMw8"
                 class="form-cta-btn"
                 target="_blank"
                 rel="noopener">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h6M15 3h6v6M10 14L21 3"/>
                </svg>
                Open membership form
              </a>
            </div>
            <p class="form-alt-note">
              Prefer to reach out directly?
              <a href="https://m.me/670694326367406" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Message us</a>
              or <a href="contact.html">send us a message</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Volunteer form -->
        <div class="form-section" id="volunteer-form">
          <div class="form-section-head">
            <div>
              <div class="form-section-title">Volunteer Registration</div>
              <div class="form-section-cn">義工登記</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-section-body">
            <div class="form-placeholder">
              <div class="form-placeholder-icon">義</div>
              <div class="form-placeholder-title">Volunteer Registration Form</div>
              <p class="form-placeholder-note">
                Click the button below to open the volunteer registration form. Tell us about yourself, your availability, and how you'd like to contribute.
              </p>
              <a href="https://forms.gle/oKc6hg7TAtNGF8yK6"
                 class="form-cta-btn"
                 target="_blank"
                 rel="noopener">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h6M15 3h6v6M10 14L21 3"/>
                </svg>
                Open volunteer form
              </a>
            </div>
            <p class="form-alt-note">
              Questions about volunteering?
              <a href="https://m.me/670694326367406" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Message us</a> anytime.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── CTA ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="section-sm section-navy" style="text-align:center;">
      <div class="container" style="max-width:600px;">
        <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:12px;">Not sure yet?</p>
        <h2 style="color:var(--rice-paper); margin-bottom:16px;">Come and see for yourself</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--muted-sky); margin-bottom:32px;">
          The best way to understand what we do is to experience it. Join us for a Sunday class or an upcoming ritual — no commitment required.
        </p>
        <div style="display:flex; gap:16px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <a href="events.html" class="btn btn-gold">See upcoming events</a>
          <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-outline-light">Ask us a question</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
